<div class="image_reel"><a href="#"><img src="/slider/mei.jpg" alt="" /></a> <a href="#"><img src="/slider/diverse.jpg" alt="" /></a> <a href="#"><img src="/slider/lgbt.jpg" alt="" /></a> <a href="#"><img src="/slider/hsi.jpg" alt="" /></a></div>
